The paper discusses a fundamental problem in various research fields like machine learning, data mining, and pattern recognition, which suggests that it could belong to multiple sub-categories. However, the focus on nearest neighbors search and hashing-based approaches makes it likely to belong to computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and databases (cs.DB) sub-categories.
